Info.about: Moeid loves to connect with learning enthusiasts and solve problems. He gains inspiration and insight through thought-provoking productive discussions. He's naturally an inquisitive lifetime learner and enjoys keeping up with current happenings in related technologies, He believes that mentoring is so deeply satisfying job/service that helps to fulfill her knowledge sharing desire and stay motivated to fuel his life long learning enthusiasm by learning/sharing along with mentees.
